App sends POST to /signup
request body is
username=daddy&password=daddy123&name=tanmay%20tiwari&			// where 32 is userid of user,daddy123 is password

---------------------------------

controller returns:
{
"result":"n1",
// if result is 0
"userid":"id",
"username":"daddy",
"name":"tanmay tiwari",
"privacy":"3"		//see privacy documentations
}

where
n1=
0:ok
1:user already exists
7:error

id=
user's new id 		(store it locally)